      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:63:35",
      "text": [
        " قُلْتُ لِأَبِي عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) فِي أَدَبِ الصَّبِيِّ وَ الْمَمْلُوكِ فَقَالَ خَمْسَةٌ أَوْ سِتَّةٌ وَ ارْفُقْ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Al Husayn Bin Muhammad, from Moala Bin Muhammad, from Al Hassan Bin Ali, from Hammad Bin Usman who said, ",
          "‘I spoke to Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> regarding disiplining of the child and the owned (slave), so he<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘Five, or six, and be kind’."
        ]
      }
